settings.title: Salicylic Acid
settings.desc: Clinically proven effective on deep pimples and blackheads and has unique skin-soothing properties.

settings.title: Niacinamide
settings.desc: A strong skin-repairing ingredient that significantly reduces enlarged pores, fine lines, and brightens dull, uneven skin.

settings.title: Centella Asiatica
settings.desc: Antioxidant, soothes inflammation, redness, and irritated skin. Firms skin while fighting breakouts and boosting collagen levels!

settings.title: Tea Tree
settings.desc: Anti-inflammatory, antimicrobial, and antiseptic for combating itchy skin and reducing redness and swelling. Helps reduce acne scars.

settings.title: Hyaluronic Acid
settings.desc: Occurs naturally in the skin. It is an excellent moisture binder, hydrates and soothes the skin, and prevents moisture loss.

settings.title: Why are microcrystals a game changer?
settings.text:
Because these tiny noninvasive microcrystals work wonders on those deep pimples that take forever to come up.

Being able to penetrate deeper layers of the skin and delivering effective active ingredients, they work like a charm reducing the pain and inflammation of underground zits!

These have helped me reduce my OCD skin-picking.

settings.title: Why you'll love it?
settings.text:
Microcrystals represent the new generation of innovations in blemish care and we strongly believe in the technology and science behind the product.

We have created a unique active ingredients formula with a 360° approach for treating zits:
✓ healing the infection
✓ alleviating inflammation
✓ hydrating the skin to avoid scarring

settings.title: When to use the microcrystals patch?
settings.text: Each time you feel a hard-to-reach and stubborn one is ready to make an "undercover" entry.

settings.title: How does it work?
settings.text:
Once the pimple patch is applied, the OMMA microcrystals completely & rapidly dissolve and deliver the unique active ingredients formula directly to the zits below the skin.

If the pimple is in the early stage, it prevents it from developing or, if the bump is already formed it brings it faster to the surface and speeds up the healing process.

settings.title: What about the price?
settings.text:
The microcrystal pimple patches may seem pricy, but for something so effective, these will actually save you money in the long run!

Just think about how much you’ll save by stopping using tiring acne routines with creams that struggle to reach deep below the skin.

settings.title: Free shipping & fulfillment info
settings.text:
We currently offer free shipping for our standard shipping method.

We ship from Salt Lake City and all orders are shipped using DHL, USPS or FEDEX. These services are fully trackable once the couriers have your order.

Shipping fees:

•Standard shipping is FREE for all orders during the Official Launch.
•For Express shipping, a flat rate of $15 is charged at checkout.

Transit time:
•For Standard Free shipping, transit time is usually between 3 and 4 Business Days from when your order is dispatched. 
•For Express shipping, transit time is usually between 1 and 2 Business Days from when your order is dispatched. 

Processing time:
•All orders are processed pending availability and payment verification.
•Orders are processed in max. 2 working days (orders placed between Friday, 2 pm, and 8 am Monday, will be processed starting on Monday).
